Package: plasmoRUtils
Title: A one-stop R Package for Plasmodium and other Apicomplexan parasite-related Bioinformatics analysis
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Rohit", "Satyam", , "rohit.satyam@kaust.edu.sa", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9311-4992")),
    person("Alberto", "Maillo", , "alberto.ruizdeinfante@kaust.edu.sa", role = c("aut", "ctb")),
    person("David", "Gomez-Cabrero", , "david.gomezcabrero@kaust.edu.sa", role = "aut"),
    person("Arnab", "Pain", , "arnab.pain@kaust.edu.sa", role = "aut")
  )
Maintainer: Rohit Satyam <rohit.satyam@kaust.edu.sa>
Description: plasmoRUtils package provides ability to access several
    specialized databases majorly for Plasmodium and several other
    apicomplexans, carry out gene ID conversions and fetch annotation for
    provided gene IDs. In addition, it also provides functions to quickly
    carry out enrichment analysis of gene expression data.
